data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers an inviting open floor plan, complete with vaulted ceilings that exude a sense of spaciousness. You'll love the generously sized primary suite, perfect for your comfort.Parking is a breeze with a convenient two-car garage, and your furry friends will thrive in the secure, fenced backyard. The best part? No HOA fees or city taxes! Plus, it's just a stone's throw away from Camp Lejeune, as well as fantastic shopping and dining options.But wait, there's more! This home has received a fresh coat of paint both inside and out as of summer 2022, giving it a vibrant and welcoming feel. Don't wait another moment - seize this opportunity and schedule your showing today! Your future home awaits.And that's not all! This home comes with fantastic bonuses: the washer and dryer are staying, along with both fridges inside and in the garage. Enjoy cozy evenings by the fire pit, and rest easy with the added smart door lock and security system with cameras. The countertops have been recently redone, and the roof comes with a transferable warranty to the new owner.  This is the complete package you've been waiting for! Call now to make it yours.
